Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.79,0:00:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon power of my ancestors\Nwas awakened within me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and I challenged our mortal enemy,\Na Magical Girl, to a round of fierce combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.08,0:00:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,One day has passed since our grand duel ended!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.08,0:00:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,G'morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.54,0:00:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad about your utter defeat yesterday, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.91,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what happened at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.00,0:00:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We were locked in combat...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's not how I remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.91,0:00:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you think about it like a soccer match,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.66,0:00:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}SHAMIKO'S PERSPECTIVE
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.58,0:00:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you got absolutely wrecked 7 points to 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}IMAGINATION\N{\an7}Nooooo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.66,0:00:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really saying that I scored a point?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.87,0:00:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to be the one to lie to myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.45,0:00:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! You're my friend, so I put in one point just for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.83,0:00:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great, Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.08,0:00:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... I'm really glad to have Anri as a friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.66,0:01:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the tale of a girl\Nwho received demonic powers overnight,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and must rise up to defeat a Magical Girl\Nin order to save her family from the grips of poverty.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.62,0:01:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Or something to that effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Demon Girl Next Door
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Just How Sporty Are You?!\N{\an8}Everything is Fluctuating
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.08,0:02:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Classic\N{\an8}Mild\N{\an8}TEA
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I was crushed yesterday\Nbecause I went in totally unprepared and untrained.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.87,0:02:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But at least now I know it's impossible\Nfor a level 1 Demon Girl to fight a level 99 Magical Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I'll just have to train myself until\NI'm strong enough to beat that Pink Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Or search for another one that might be weaker!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.70,0:03:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Just FYI, I'm relatively weak\Ncompared to other Magical Girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.00,0:03:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.45,0:03:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tap\N{\an8}Tap
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.83,0:03:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tap\N{\an8}Tap
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wassup!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.54,0:03:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,The Pink Magical Girl is back again!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been here for a while now...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.95,0:03:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Pink Magical Girl! Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.50,0:03:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in Class A aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.45,0:03:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes girls who awaken to demon powers\Nget swallowed by the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.08,0:03:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,and become a monstrous problem,\Nso I came to check up on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.00,0:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}DARKNESS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.20,0:03:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sploosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.66,0:03:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}DARKNESS
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.12,0:03:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean a "monstrous problem"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.95,0:03:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, did you just say that you were "relatively weak"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.12,0:03:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I heard that you saved the world once...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because I had very strong allies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So aside from the Pink Magical Girl, there are even\Nstronger ones just lurking around every corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.04,0:03:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, you don't have to keep describing me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just call me "Momo."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.12,0:04:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,From the looks of it you don't seem like\Nyou're going to get swallowed up by the darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.87,0:03:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Such horror...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.37,0:04:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Shamiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.04,0:04:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Shami- Shadow Mistress Yuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.00,0:04:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, "Sha-mi-ko."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.12,0:04:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}S\N{\an8}N\N{\an8}A\N{\an8}R\N{\an8}L
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.70,0:04:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Pink Magical Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.50,0:04:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Pink Magical Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Just call me "Momo."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that weird nickname catches on in the\Nentire school, I'm going to drain all the blood from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, when class ends, I will defeat you\Nat the riverbank behind the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait, and keep that precious blood pumping!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.50,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not really interested, to be honest...\NI'm through with doing all the Magical Girl stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Is your fear getting\Nthe better of you, Pink Magical Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's "Momo."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you planning to finish your training\Nbefore school ends today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.33,0:04:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you really get that much stronger in just six hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.41,0:04:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,How about sometime during the afternoon\Nthis weekend instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Afternoon this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Training Room\N{\an8}ENDURANCE MONTH\N{\an8}Build your brawn and become\Na tough young woman.\NLet your muscles do the talking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.33,0:04:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... I should have planned better,\Nthe deadline for my training just became this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.83,0:04:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,How heavy do you want your dumbbells?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:04:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,1 pound please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.37,0:05:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I already got permission to use\Nthe training room from our teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.16,0:05:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get down to business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the Pink Magical Girl also uses that training room...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. I think you could train\Njust by using water bottles instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.58,0:05:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! With just 1-pound weights it doesn't make sense\Nto even bother with the training room!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.45,0:05:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get down to business!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.37,0:05:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Battle with the Pink Magical Girl
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.41,0:05:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Beat the Magical Girl!!\N{\an8}Training Menu\N{\an8}(Make sure to do everything!!)\N{\an8}Plank - 30 Seconds\N{\an8}Squats - 15 times\N{\an8}Take a 30 minute break\N{\an8}Lift Dumbbells - 5 times\N{\an8}Punch practice - 10 times
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, the day has finally arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I'm off to murderize the Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.50,0:05:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck out there, Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.79,0:05:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Tama River
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess your fear didn't get\Nthe better of you today, Pink Magical Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me "Momo."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.12,0:05:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}TANNED
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.29,0:05:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you always been that tan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.16,0:06:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You said "weekend" but didn't specify\NSaturday or Sunday, so I waited here yesterday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.45,0:06:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In the hot summer sun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.91,0:06:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, I should have specified.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.91,0:06:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No worries, it didn't even\Ncross my mind until Friday night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But it would really help if I knew\Nhow to get a hold of you in times like these.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My number is 042...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}New Contact\N{\an8}Shamirin
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I told my mortal enemy my phone number.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough! I've been waiting a long time for this day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've spent long hours training\Nin my house just to defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.16,0:06:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you've lost a few pounds,\Nand the muscles in your chest are starting to fill out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.95,0:06:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... ah... really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.20,0:06:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I think the muscles in your triceps\Nare looking especially nice. Truly wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.16,0:06:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I get the feeling you might ramble on\N{\an8}so let's cut this short!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:51.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.29,0:06:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you need to warm-up first?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.79,0:06:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.04,0:06:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.50,0:07:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You really should. Let's do warm-ups together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.12,0:07:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you seem so enthusiastic about all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.83,0:07:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}BONK      BONK      BONK      BONK      BONK      BONK
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.54,0:07:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,At the very least, you should do some stretches.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.04,0:07:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Sigh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.29,0:07:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You hurt yourself before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.95,0:07:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You might even tear a ligament in your tail this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A ligament in my tail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.87,0:07:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}RECORDS OF THE THREE KINGDOMS
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mikan
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.37,0:07:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like Cao Cao when he conquered\NNorthern China after the fall of the Han Dynasty...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.62,0:07:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that sis is engaged in a round of mortal combat\Nwith that Magical Girl right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't raise your heel in back like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.50,0:07:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you've finished the basics. Now, let's go for a run.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.12,0:07:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.16,0:07:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you really should warm-up first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even an absolute beginner\Ncan run 2 miles if they keep a solid pace.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.75,0:07:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,2 miles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.08,0:07:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not coming, then I'll go by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,W-wait! You're fleeing from our battle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.00,0:07:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.58,0:08:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.41,0:08:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,For the first mile we'll keep a 12-minute pace,\Nand for the second mile we'll do 10. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.08,0:08:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.37,0:08:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.87,0:08:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why exactly am I running with my mortal enemy\Nalong the river bank at sunset?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.87,0:08:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks, this sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.33,0:08:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There are people out here? Taking their dog for a walk...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.29,0:08:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see a bridge...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.04,0:08:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This sucks... this sucks... this sucks... this sucks... this su-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.04,0:08:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.37,0:08:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.45,0:08:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:08:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like everything is fluctuating!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamiko was experiencing her very first runner's high.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The current of the flowing river does not cease,\Nand yet the water is not the same water as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.16,0:09:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}A good run always makes you feel alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It helps us forget all the bad things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.79,0:09:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The foam that floats on stagnant pools\Nis also just another part of the impermanence of our-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.70,0:09:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Remind me, why are we running again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't remember, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've started to sense... my inner potential...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, so how about we keep running\Nuntil we hit the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in the middle of the mountains right now, though?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Rage!\NAh! I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.50,0:09:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}RAGE!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.79,0:09:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I just remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Our battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't run that much anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot, you remembered.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get it over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.66,0:09:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Just finished warming up\N{\an7}Totally burned out
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Want to postpone it until after tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.87,0:10:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.54,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a sports drink that's been diluted down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.25,0:10:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I added some glucose to it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.91,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why diluted?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sports drinks on the market today are not actually\Noptimized for the necessary osmotic pressure
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,needed after completing a workout.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, they're made stronger than necessary\Nand so by diluting them you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.45,0:10:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Waaah! Forget I asked! But thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.83,0:10:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing led to the other and we ended up\Nrunning 3 miles. You did great, Shamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, we ran 3 whole miles!\NThat's the first time I've done that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:31.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? 3 miles...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.83,0:10:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}3 More Miles (4km)\N{\an8}To get Home
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.41,0:10:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to keep running for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.70,0:10:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... Momo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Please lend me fare... for the train ride back...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.83,0:10:53.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is $5.00 enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.45,0:10:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Air-conditioned Car
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.66,0:11:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the AC feels great...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.58,0:11:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Sigh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.20,0:11:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...means you've...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...won...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.29,0:11:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your patronage.\NThis train has reached the end of the line and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Deep Inner\N{\an8}Tama Station
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the heck am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.25,0:11:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, Shamiko! Start out by returning\Nthe $5.00 that you borrowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:12:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}YOSHIDA
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm headed to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a good day, Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So tell me, Yuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.25,0:12:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How is progress coming on your mission\Nto subdue a Magical Girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, well I found a Magical Girl to defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.45,0:12:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And I challenged her to combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.95,0:12:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,And then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.95,0:12:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We ran along the river bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.95,0:12:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? You ran...? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.00,0:12:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really understand why, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:29.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, I just found myself out on a jog!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.16,0:12:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always been a frail girl since birth,\Nnot to mention stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.50,0:12:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured that going down this path\Nwould not be an easy thing for you, but....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.29,0:12:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...it seems I'm going to have to provide you\Nwith some assistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.70,0:12:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I noticed you added and tried to cover up\Nthat little insult... but thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to provide you\Nwith extra funds to defeat the Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.37,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your allowance is going up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.70,0:12:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your allowance has always been $1.20 a month, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.75,0:12:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,...guess what!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.16,0:13:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm giving you a big boost to $5.00 a month!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.62,0:13:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaaaat?! Is that really okay?\NAre you sure that's not too much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.12,0:13:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}5 DOLLARS\N{\an8}(500 YEN)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.95,0:13:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the Light Clan's "$400 a Month" curse\Nwas making us live paycheck-to-paycheck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.50,0:13:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right. I've managed to set some funds aside\Nin a secret savings account.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.54,0:13:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I'm going to quit buying\Ninto those damn lotteries I never win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But Mom! What about those stamps\Nyou accumulated for buying mushrooms?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless I win, it's just a waste of postage to send them in!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.12,0:13:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da! Take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.75,0:13:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My allowance got raised\Nto help me beat the Magical Girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.37,0:13:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Check it out, it's freshly minted!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.33,0:13:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Congrats, Shamiko!\NNow you can buy all the candy you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that your purse...?\NWow! Congrats, Shamiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you can buy all the candy you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.79,0:13:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't buy any candy!\NI will use this to defeat that Magical Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.29,0:13:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really not going to buy any candy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.83,0:13:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I will not! I must bring an end to the Magical Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.29,0:13:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I beat her with just $5.00...?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.91,0:14:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,After I eat some candy, maybe I can use\Nthe wrappers to subdue her! Or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.45,0:14:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can Shark Tank my way into getting more funds...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.25,0:14:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamiko, your willpower is as weak as your punch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.79,0:14:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Momo! What good timing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.33,0:14:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm returning the bottle you lent me the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.41,0:14:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks. You could have\Ntaken your time though, I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.25,0:14:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You might not, but I certainly do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.16,0:14:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never become a respectful Demon Girl if I'm\Nalways borrowing from the likes of a Magical Girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.08,0:14:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's admirable, Shamiko. Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could return that $5.00 I lent you\Nfor the train, while you're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.25,0:14:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I seem to have exactly the right amount,\Nfor some reason....
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, just forget about it! Sorry, you can keep it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.16,0:14:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,D-don't insult me! Just take it and don't worry about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really know what's going on,\Nbut I can clearly see you crying, Shamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just eye juice! They are not tears!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, come on! Just take the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Momochiyo, there are some complicated reasons,\Nbut this girl and her family are flat broke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.00,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Look! It's just eye juice! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.04,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's why she's got so much eye juice right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's make it a payment plan\Nwith 10 separate installments. 50 cents a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.62,0:15:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't just decide that without the approval\Nof the person in debt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But then you can buy candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.54,0:15:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take the payment plan, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.79,0:15:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Although, if we do this it means\Nyou won't be able to fight me for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.45,0:15:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.95,0:15:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't you feel just terribad for beating up\Nthe person who you were indebted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, if you take me out of the picture now,\Nit's only going to cause you bigger problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.95,0:15:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to die before you paid me back,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.20,0:15:36.95,Default,,0,0,0,,you would be haunted by\Nthe lingering debt for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I-is that really how it works?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Something seems wrong about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not wrong. If that happens,\Nyou'll become a bankrupt demon for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"Bankrupt"...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want to be bankrupt, Shamiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.20,0:15:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be bankrupt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then do your best and pay me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.70,0:15:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.70,0:15:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:16:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Grr. I feel like I was tricked.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.62,0:16:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you ask me the whole thing\Nwas pretty straightforward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.04,0:16:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You're really gullible, Shamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think that's for the best, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.87,0:16:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,With 10 whole months, you can train really hard and\Nbecome strong enough to give Momochiyo a real fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.75,0:16:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-you're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.58,0:16:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, I'll use my remaining $4.50\Nto find an idea to help me win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.41,0:16:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You should use it to make a weapon.\NMaybe a projectile one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Great idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:31.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A weapon that works on a Magical Girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.62,0:16:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try using a trail of Smarties\Nto lure an aggressive dog to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice! You're still hung up on buying candy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.20,0:16:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what a pirate's lost treasure looks like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.37,0:16:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I dreaming right now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to find a weapon,\Nthen this is the place to look!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.66,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.08,0:16:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...why is Momo coming with us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.33,0:17:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you're not thinking clearly, Shamiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know you're going to waste your precious funds\Nto make something super useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not THAT stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll go ahead and ask,\Nwhat are those chopsticks and rubber bands for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.41,0:17:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing wrong with making a rubber band gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:16.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll go put them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.25,0:17:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}ONE\N{\an8}HIT\N{\an8}KILL\N{\an8}$35.00\N{\an8}(3,500 YEN)
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.45,0:17:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,All the weapons cost even more than I imagined...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}UDON GARDEN
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamiko, check out the food court!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tempt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.58,0:17:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Their self-serve udon is really tasty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.87,0:17:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Go, go! Go, go! Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse to go to the food court!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.20,0:17:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet they have that needlessly\Nextravagant ice cream! And udon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.20,0:17:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I just know it's all delicious food\Nthat doesn't actually make you full!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.58,0:17:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:18:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}UDON GARDEN
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's wrong! I meant I don't want to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.54,0:18:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't fight the urge! Anri! Ogura! Momo!\NSomebody stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.25,0:18:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to brainstorm new ideas\Nthen you need carbohydrates!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.62,0:18:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Part of your budget should go into food\Nto assure you have enough energy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take the chikuwa tempura\Nand add it to your plate, like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That makes sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Guh... how did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.45,0:18:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's "white meat" tempura?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.29,0:18:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Chicken, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.12,0:18:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Do you mind if I have a bite?\NIs this just another one of the Magical Girl's schemes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To get me addicted to this fancy food court\Nand completely drain my financial resources?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.04,0:18:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Then I'll give you one of my fish tempura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let her manipulate me like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want some too, Shamiko? It's really yummy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind trading for my chikuwa tempura...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.66,0:18:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's impressive that you drank all the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.41,0:18:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too delicious to waste!\NThere were lots of tempura bits at the bottom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.00,0:19:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I can't even afford to make a rubber band gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.33,0:19:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,This udon and chikuwa tempura meal\Nleft me with only $1.20 left to my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.58,0:19:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}$1.20\N{\an8}( 120 Yen )
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}All drinks $1.20\N{\an7}(120 yen)
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.70,0:19:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamiko, are you thirsty? You drank so much salty broth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.29,0:19:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't trick me into buying anything else!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.54,0:19:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really relieved, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.75,0:19:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Your family doesn't seem to have a lot of money\Nand you always leave so quick after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a lot of fun watching you\Nchow down on that udon today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Anri...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.83,0:19:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm sorry we pushed you into doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.58,0:19:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thinking about it, Anri is always\Nreally busy with her club activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I usually go straight home after school,\Nshe's always chatted with me even before I grew horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Has she been going out of her way\Nto watch out for me this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.91,0:20:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I'll start thinking more seriously\Nabout how to solve your problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.54,0:20:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? You mean you haven't been...?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised that Anri would do\Nso much just for little old me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.00,0:20:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamiko?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.33,0:20:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi-yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.79,0:20:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.37,0:20:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I chug it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Cough, cough, cough... burp! Cough, cough!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,To be perfectly honest... burp,\NI also... really enjoyed myself, burp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.29,0:20:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll even come back next month, burp,\Nif you really want me to, Anri. Burp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.00,0:20:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.62,0:20:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But don't push yourself too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.54,0:20:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamiko has absolutely no money left for the month.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.75,0:20:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Absolutely No Money Left
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.95,0:20:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You have none of your allowance left now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.41,0:21:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I was feeling thirsty anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.83,0:21:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, I realized that I've been\Nmaking you worry about me this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamiko...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll work hard to become a great demon\Nwho notices lots of other stuff too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I think group outings like these are going\Nto become how I encourage myself to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hopefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.37,0:21:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.16,0:21:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.95,0:21:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a... free water dispenser?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.87,0:21:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think this means you've won!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh, me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.83,0:21:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Do your best, Shamiko! You can save a lot if you\Ndon't spend on drinks and utilize free resources instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,A dunce... A complete dunce!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.70,0:21:54.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How the hell did she end up in such a mess?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.33,0:21:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,And why does she have\Nsuch a careless look on her face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.04,0:22:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not taking this seriously at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.58,0:22:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,She's just way too pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.95,0:22:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems I shall have to set her on the right path\Npersonally, with my own touch of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.87,0:22:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Just you wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.70,0:22:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My little descendant!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.54,0:22:34.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The Demon Girl Next Door
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.04,0:24:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.50,0:23:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuko, my adorable descendant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.66,0:23:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Who're you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.58,0:23:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your great ancestor! The founder of the Dark Clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.95,0:23:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'm going to share with you\Nour many precious secrets!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.54,0:24:00.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My ancestor...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.37,0:24:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Shamiko, let's go and practice using projectile weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.83,0:24:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Preview\N{\an8}Your weapon was stolen!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.37,0:24:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap, it's Momo again! I'm going home!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.95,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an7}Preview\N{\an7}Nightmare or Forebear?! The Doorstop of Darkness Descends
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.45,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not leaving until you shoot something.